          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39796926/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39796926/" class="">第一部分 特性/身份问题</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/149267546/" class=" " title="34mblue">34mblue</a>
                (岁月长，衣裳薄)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39796926">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">公民的民族主义 VS 种族的民族主义
种族身份改变不了，文化身份可以改变</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-10-22 05:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                公民的民族主义 VS 种族的民族主义<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>种族身份改变不了，文化身份可以改变
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
